      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我需要确认一下顺序：feature分支要在commit a之后切出来，然后在feature上提交f，同时main继续往前走到b，最后再把feature合并进来。这个时序对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch feature",
